measurements.description: Three flowers on three erect 10-cm inflorescences; dorsal sepal reflexed basally, slightly cupped, cream, overlaid chartreuse, dark chartreuse veins basal half, cordovan mid-line extending into cream apical area; synsepal light chartreuse, striped dark chartreuse; petals undulate margins, chartruse veined and blushed cordovan, darker superior surface, hirsute basally; pouch light chartrause overlaid light rose; staminode yellow, umbo chartreuse; substance medium; texture glossy.
